{
  "_comment": "Role -> model routing. This is where each model's strengths are used: a strong model voices the narrator and major NPCs; a fast/cheap model handles ambient NPCs, world events, the referee and summaries; the director is free/local. With no API keys, every role transparently falls back to the deterministic 'mock' provider so the simulation always runs. Set OPENAI_API_KEY / ANTHROPIC_API_KEY to enable real models, and edit the models below to taste.",
